---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Button from '../components/Button.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About Edi — DEMWeb Studio"
  description="DEMWeb Studio is run by Edi M., a full-stack developer building fast, honest websites for small businesses and freelancers worldwide."
>
  <section class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 py-16 sm:px-6 sm:py-24 lg:px-8">
    <h1 class="text-center text-4xl font-medium tracking-tight text-ink sm:text-left sm:text-5xl">
      About DEMWeb Studio
    </h1>

    <div class="mt-8 space-y-6 text-lg text-ink-secondary">
      <p>
        Hi, I'm Edi — I design and build websites for small businesses and freelancers who need a site that
        actually works for them, not just one that looks fine in a screenshot.
      </p>
      <p>
        I started DEMWeb Studio after watching the same story play out too many times: a business owner pays for a
        website and ends up with something slow, generic, and nearly impossible to find in search — usually built
        from a template with more features than the business ever needed, and less performance than it deserved.
      </p>
      <p>
        I've spent the last five years working as a full-stack developer, trained through Software University
        across frontend and backend development. Separately, I've also completed certified courses in AI prompt
        engineering and conversational AI. DEMWeb Studio is where that background comes together into one clear
        focus: fast, hand-built websites with SEO built in from day one, not bolted on afterward.
      </p>
      <p>
        Clients are typically small companies and independent freelancers who need a site that actually represents
        their business and gets found in search — not an agency-scale engagement with agency-scale overhead. You
        work directly with me, start to finish, no handoffs.
      </p>
      <p>
        I work with clients worldwide and communicate in English, German, or Bulgarian, whichever's easiest for
        you. My hours aren't locked to a strict 9-to-5, so I'm usually able to fit calls and updates around your
        schedule rather than the other way around — useful if we're not in the same timezone.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-12 rounded-2xl border border-border bg-card p-8 sm:p-10">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-medium text-ink">How projects run</h2>
      <p class="mt-3 text-ink-secondary">
        Every project follows the same five-step process, from first conversation to post-launch support.
      </p>
      <a
        href="/process"
        class="mt-4 inline-flex items-center gap-1 text-sm font-medium text-teal hover:underline"
      >
        See how I work →
      </a>
    </div>

    <div
      class="mt-12 flex flex-col items-center gap-4 text-center sm:flex-row sm:items-center sm:justify-between sm:text-left"
    >
      <p class="text-ink-secondary">Have a project in mind?</p>
      <Button href="/contact">Get a Free Call</Button>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
